@context: E-commerce purchase flow on SauceDemo
@title: swag-labs-checkout

# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FEATURES DEMONSTRATED:
#
#   Auto-Nav annotations (# 📍 Auto-Nav: ...)
#                       — When "auto_annotate": true in
#                         manul_engine_configuration.json, the engine
#                         automatically inserts these comments into .hunt
#                         files whenever the page URL changes. Page names
#                         come from pages.json; unmapped pages show the URL.
#                         These comments are informational — the engine
#                         does not execute them.
#
#   NEAR 'Anchor'       — Contextual qualifier. Biases element resolution
#                         by Euclidean distance to a resolved anchor.
#                         Used here: Click 'Add to cart' near 'Sauce Labs
#                         Fleece Jacket' — the engine first resolves the
#                         jacket text, then picks the closest 'Add to cart'
#                         button.
#
#   VERIFY ... is present
#                       — Assertion after each significant navigation.
#                         Best practice: always verify the expected page
#                         state before continuing.
#
#   Full E2E flow       — Login → browse → add to cart → checkout → verify.
#                         This is the classic pattern for E-commerce tests.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------------

STEP 1: Login
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: https://www.saucedemo.com/
    NAVIGATE to https://www.saucedemo.com/
    Fill 'Username' with 'standard_user'
    Fill 'Password' with 'secret_sauce'
    Click 'Login' button

STEP 2: Add item to cart
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: Products Catalog
    VERIFY that 'Products' is present
    # NEAR qualifier: resolves the 'Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket' text first,
    # then prefers the matching 'Add to cart' button in the same product card,
    # using both visual distance and DOM container affinity.
    Click 'Add to cart' near 'Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket'

STEP 3: Review cart
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: Shopping Cart
    Click the 'Shopping cart' link
    VERIFY that 'Sauce Labs Fleece Jacket' is present
    Click 'Checkout' button

STEP 4: Fill shipping info
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: Checkout: Your Info
    Fill 'First Name' with 'FirstName'
    Fill 'Last Name' with 'LastName'
    Fill 'Zip/Postal Code' with '49000'
    Click 'Continue' button

STEP 5: Complete order
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: Checkout: Overview
    Click 'Finish' button
    # 📍 Auto-Nav: Checkout: Complete
    VERIFY that 'Thank you for your order!' is present
DONE.
